items.title: Chernobyl radiation shield hit by Russian drone, Ukraine says
items.description: There has been no increase in radiation levels at the plant this morning, Ukraine's president says.

items.title: Pope to be admitted to hospital for bronchitis
items.description: The Pope has had bronchitis symptoms for several days leading to other officials reading his speeches.

items.title: LA vehicle swept into ocean as rain hits fire-ravaged area
items.description: Debris and mud flow pushes a fire department car into the Pacific as a rainstorm lashed LA county.

items.title: DR Congo singer killed filming video in conflict city
items.description: Delcat Idengo, well-known for his songs critical of all sides in the fighting, died in Goma.

items.title: What we know about suspected car attack in Munich
items.description: A 24-year-old Afghan asylum seeker drove at a group of people and injured at least 28, German police say.
